      <div style="font-size:3rem;color:white;font-weight:bold;">25</div>
      <div style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Jahre am Markt</div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <div style="font-size:3rem;color:white;font-weight:bold;">40000</div>
      <div style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Beraterstunden</div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <div style="font-size:3rem;color:white;font-weight:bold;">95</div>
      <div style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Kundenzufriedenheit</div>
